---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap');

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --black: #0a0a0a;
    --white: #fafaf8;
    --gray-light: #e8e8e4;
    --gray-mid: #9a9a94;
    --gray-dark: #3a3a36;
    --serif: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'DM Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    --rule: 1px solid #0a0a0a;
    --rule-light: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
  }

  body {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    height: 44px;
  }
  .nav-left { display: flex; gap: 2rem; }
  .nav-center { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .nav-right { display: flex; gap: 2rem; justify-content: flex-end; }
  nav a {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--black);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  nav a:hover { color: var(--gray-mid); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    margin-top: 44px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
    min-height: 90vh;
  }
  .hero-left {
    border-right: var(--rule);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--black);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .book-cover {
    background: var(--black);
    border: 2px solid #2a2a2a;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 280px;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94);
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #1a1a1a, 16px 16px 0 #111;
  }
  .book-cover:hover { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(-1deg); }
  .book-cover h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .book-author {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .book-cover-line {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 3.5rem;
    left: 2rem; right: 2rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: #2a2a2a;
  }

  .hero-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 3rem;
  }
  .hero-right-top h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 400;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    max-width: 340px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-bottom {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: var(--rule-light);
  }
  .preorder-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: var(--rule);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--black);
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }
  .preorder-btn:hover { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); }
  .preorder-btn .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .preorder-btn:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .square-marker {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--black);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── VISUAL MASTERY ── */
  .mastery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
  }
  .mastery-label {
    border-right: var(--rule);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .mastery-content {
    padding: 0;
  }
  .mastery-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
  }
  .mastery-col-label {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
  }
  .mastery-col-label:first-child { border-right: var(--rule); }
  .mastery-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule-light);
  }
  .mastery-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .mastery-cell {
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
  }
  .mastery-cell:first-child {
    border-right: var(--rule);
    color: var(--black);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ── GLIMPSE ── */
  .glimpse {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
  }
  .glimpse-label {
    border-right: var(--rule);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .glimpse-label h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .glimpse-label p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .glimpse-chapters {
    padding: 0;
  }
  .chapter-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule-light);
    transition: background 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .chapter-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .chapter-row:hover { background: #f4f4f0; }
  .chapter-num {
    padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    border-right: var(--rule-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 1.8rem;
  }
  .chapter-title {
    padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .chapter-title em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── AUTHOR SPREAD ── */
  .author-spread {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
    min-height: 60vh;
    background: var(--black);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .author-img-col {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .author-img-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2a2a2a 40%, #0a0a0a 100%);
    position: relative;
  }
  /* grainy texture overlay */
  .author-img-placeholder::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.15'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.4;
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  }
  .author-monogram {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    color: var(--white);
    opacity: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    pointer-events: none;
    mix-blend-mode: difference;
  }
  .author-text-col {
    border-left: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .author-text-col p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #9a9a94;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 320px;
  }
  .author-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
  }
  .stat-item {}
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #666660;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* ── PULL QUOTE ── */
  .pull-quote-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .pull-quote-marker {
    border-right: var(--rule);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .pull-quote-marker p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .pull-quote-main {
    padding: 3rem;
  }
  .pull-quote-main blockquote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .pull-quote-sub {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: var(--rule-light);
  }
  .pull-quote-sub-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .pull-quote-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .pull-stat {}
  .pull-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .pull-stat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
  .testimonials {
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
  }
  .testimonials-header {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    border: var(--rule);
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-right: var(--rule);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .testimonial-card:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .testimonial-card:hover { background: #f4f4f0; }
  .quote-mark {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    flex: 1;
  }
  .testimonial-meta {
    border-top: var(--rule-light);
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  .testimonial-name {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .testimonial-role {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }
  .testimonial-num {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ── CTA FOOTER ── */
  .cta-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
  }
  .cta-left {
    padding: 5rem 3rem;
    border-right: var(--rule);
  }
  .cta-left h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .cta-left h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .cta-left .cta-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .cta-right {
    padding: 5rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .cta-right p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 320px;
  }
  .cta-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .cta-links a {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--black);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }
  .cta-links a:hover { border-color: var(--black); }

  /* ── NAMEPLATE ── */
  .nameplate {
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: var(--rule);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .nameplate-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 12rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: clip;
  }

  /* ── MICRO INTERACTIONS ── */
  .chapter-row {
    position: relative;
  }
  .chapter-row::after {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    right: 2rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(-8px);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .chapter-row:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(0);
  }

  /* scroll reveal */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    * { transition: none !important; }
  }

  /* ── MOBILE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 0 1rem; }
    .nav-left, .nav-right { display: none; }

    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .hero-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule); padding: 2rem; min-height: 50vw; }
    .book-cover { max-width: 200px; }
    .hero-right { padding: 2rem; }

    .mastery { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mastery-label { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule); }
    .mastery-header, .mastery-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mastery-cell:first-child { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule-light); }

    .glimpse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .glimpse-label { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule); }
    .chapter-row { grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr; }

    .author-spread { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .author-img-col { min-height: 40vw; }
    .author-text-col { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a; }

    .pull-quote-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pull-quote-marker { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule); }
    .pull-quote-sub { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .testimonial-card { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule); }
    .testimonial-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .cta-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--rule); padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .cta-right { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .cta-links { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }

    .nameplate { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
  }
</style>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-left">
    <a href="#">home</a>
    <a href="#">about</a>
    <a href="#">artwork</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-center">JH</div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <a href="#">challenge</a>
    <a href="#">approach</a>
    <a href="#">contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="book-cover">
      <div>
        <h1>Unseen Connections:<br/>The Art of Creating Visual Stories</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="book-cover-line"></div>
      <p class="book-author">JAMES HOLT</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right reveal">
    <div class="hero-right-top">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">The Thinking Behind Design</p>
      <h2>Unseen Connections : The Art of Creating Visual Stories</h2>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Unseen Connections explores the thinking behind impactful design — uncovering how clarity, purpose, and considered decisions create lasting meaning for an audience.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bottom">
      <a href="#" class="preorder-btn">
        PRE-ORDER NOW <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <div class="square-marker"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VISUAL MASTERY -->
<section class="mastery reveal">
  <div class="mastery-label">A Guide to Visual Mastery</div>
  <div class="mastery-content">
    <div class="mastery-header">
      <div class="mastery-col-label">FRAMEWORK</div>
      <div class="mastery-col-label">INSIGHT</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mastery-row">
      <div class="mastery-cell">How to craft a memorable brand story through design</div>
      <div class="mastery-cell">Craft memorable brand stories through design, understanding storytelling's role in audience connection.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mastery-row">
      <div class="mastery-cell">The art of creative direction and why it matters</div>
      <div class="mastery-cell">Creative direction shapes not only visuals, but also clarity, perception, and brand frameworks every decision.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mastery-row">
      <div class="mastery-cell">The role of simplicity and boldness in impactful visuals</div>
      <div class="mastery-cell">Explore how simplicity and boldness work together to create clarity and make brand visuals every decision.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mastery-row">
      <div class="mastery-cell">How design choices create lasting emotional connections with audiences</div>
      <div class="mastery-cell">Design decisions influence emotion, creating design connections that stay with audiences to shape their first impression.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- GLIMPSE INTO PAGES -->
<section class="glimpse">
  <div class="glimpse-label reveal">
    <h3>A Glimpse Into the Pages</h3>
    <p>Unseen Connections offers a life-altering perspective on design — new ideas and the thinking behind relevant and clarity-reaching experiences.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="glimpse-chapters">
    <div class="chapter-row reveal">
      <span class="chapter-num">CHAPTER 1</span>
      <div class="chapter-title">The Power of First Impressions — Creating memorable brand identities.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="chapter-row reveal">
      <span class="chapter-num">CHAPTER 2</span>
      <div class="chapter-title">From Brief to Vision — How to turn a concept into an artistic direction.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="chapter-row reveal">
      <span class="chapter-num">CHAPTER 3</span>
      <div class="chapter-title">Leading the Charge — Managing creativity in teams.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="chapter-row reveal">
      <span class="chapter-num">CHAPTER 4</span>
      <div class="chapter-title">Designing for the Future — The evolving role of an Art Director in digital landscapes.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- AUTHOR SPREAD -->
<section class="author-spread reveal">
  <div class="author-img-col">
    <div class="author-img-placeholder">
      <div class="author-monogram">JH</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="author-text-col">
    <p>Helping individuals get deeper forward-thinking clarity through this book, together with our supporting community design. No theories, just clear and practical experience on their brand new world opening.</p>
    <p>Showing technical knowledge through comprehensive design. By focusing on making advanced design topics accessible, James Holt has built a global creative authority for forward-thinking leaders.</p>
    <div class="author-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">50+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Global Projects</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">10+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Industries Shaped</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PULL QUOTE -->
<section class="pull-quote-section">
  <div class="pull-quote-marker reveal">
    <div class="square-marker"></div>
    <p>James Holt approaches the design of thinking — seeing design and clarity as deeply important for everyone.</p>
    <div class="square-marker"></div>
    <p>Early readers confirm in their ideas that James has clarity and vision to make only creative work.</p>
  </div>
